text: Varna is a hamlet (and census-designated place) located in Tompkins County, New York, USA. It is within the Town of Dryden. Fall Creek in Varna, New York Varna is located near the west town line on New York State Route 366 (Dryden Road). Fall Creek flows past the town to Cayuga Lake. ==References== ==External links== * Varna Community Association * Varna Volunteer Fire Company, Inc.
